title: The Walking Dead Just Proved The Strength of Its Universe
author: Reel Talk
comment: I think a Black Comedy show based in TWD universe would freshen things up for people. It wouldn't be a grim for casual viewers, and have a bit more fun with the IP.
eh boy... you really need to watch other shows. This season is a complet disaster.
description:
The Walking Dead Just Proved The Strength of Its Universe. Season 10C has proven that AMC's extended universe for TWD can work by focusing on characters, small plots, and incremental development.
